---
// Accessibility statement (EN) for Caleta Suites Tenerife.
//
// NEW URL: /en/accessibility/ (allowed addition — does not modify any existing
// URL). Follows the W3C WAI 10-section template from the wcag-aa-aaa skill.
//
// Declared real status: FULL conformance with WCAG 2.2 level AA. Colour contrast
// additionally meets level AAA (1.4.6): the brand blue was darkened to #37597C
// (7.29:1) and all text reaches >=7:1. This was an authorised deviation from the
// exact visual replica for accessibility reasons (see docs/deviations.md). Full AAA
// is not claimed because not every AAA criterion has been verified.
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

// Statement date (review on every audit). ISO format for the JSON-LD.
const fechaDeclaracion = '2026-06-14';
const fechaLegible = '14 June 2026';

// Page-specific WebPage JSON-LD (richer than the Layout LodgingBusiness):
// declares partial conformance and the real accessibility summary.
const jsonLdPagina = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'WebPage',
  name: 'Accessibility statement — Caleta Suites Tenerife',
  url: 'https://caletasuitestenerife.com/en/accessibility/',
  inLanguage: 'en',
  dateModified: fechaDeclaracion,
  accessibilityFeature: ['alternativeText', 'structuredNavigation', 'readingOrder', 'highContrastDisplay'],
  accessibilityHazard: 'none',
  accessibilitySummary:
    'Fully conformant with WCAG 2.2 level AA. Colour contrast meets level AAA (1.4.6): all text reaches a contrast ratio of at least 7:1.',
};
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility statement — Caleta Suites Tenerife"
  description="Accessibility statement for Caleta Suites Tenerife: WCAG 2.2 conformance status, known limitations, contact and complaints procedure."
  lang="en"
  altPath="/accesibilidad/"
  jsonLd={[jsonLdPagina]}
>
  <article style="max-width:72ch;margin:0 auto;padding:2rem 1.25rem;line-height:1.6;">
    <h1>Accessibility statement</h1>

    {/* 1 — Commitment */}
    <section id="commitment">
      <h2>1. Our commitment</h2>
      <p>
        At Caleta Suites Tenerife we want everyone to be able to find information and book
        their accommodation regardless of their abilities or the technology they use. That is
        why we work to make this website accessible in line with the Web Content Accessibility
        Guidelines (WCAG) 2.2.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* 2 — Conformance status */}
    <section id="status">
      <h2>2. Conformance status</h2>
      <p>
        This website is <strong>fully conformant</strong> with WCAG 2.2 level
        <strong>AA</strong>. In addition, <strong>colour contrast meets level AAA</strong>
        (criterion 1.4.6): all text has a contrast ratio of at least 7:1. We do not claim full
        AAA conformance because some criteria at that level are outside the verified scope.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* 3 — Measures to support accessibility */}
    <section id="measures">
      <h2>3. Measures to support accessibility</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Semantic structure with page regions (header, navigation, main content and footer).</li>
        <li>Skip link to jump straight to the main content with the keyboard.</li>
        <li>Visible, high-contrast focus indicator on all interactive elements.</li>
        <li>AAA-level colour contrast (≥ 7:1) on all text, including the brand blue.</li>
        <li>Alternative text on informative images and a coherent reading order.</li>
        <li>Page language declared for screen readers.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    {/* 4 — Non-accessible content / known limitations */}
    <section id="non-accessible-content">
      <h2>4. Non-accessible content</h2>
      <p>
        No non-accessible content has been identified in the site's own pages. The brand blue
        contrast limitation reported in earlier versions has been <strong>resolved</strong>: the
        shade was darkened to a blue that meets level AAA (contrast ratio ≥ 7:1) both as text and
        on buttons.
      </p>
      <p>
        Content served by third parties (the embedded booking engine, maps or external widgets)
        remains outside our control, as its accessibility depends on the providers (see section 5).
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* 5 — Scope */}
    <section id="scope">
      <h2>5. Scope of this statement</h2>
      <p>
        This statement covers the pages published on the
        <code>caletasuitestenerife.com</code> domain. It does not cover content served by third
        parties (the embedded booking engine, maps or external widgets), whose accessibility
        depends on their providers.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* 6 — Evaluation methodology */}
    <section id="methodology">
      <h2>6. Evaluation methodology</h2>
      <p>The accessibility of this site is evaluated through:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Automated analysis with axe-core and Lighthouse.</li>
        <li>Manual inspection of the accessibility tree and keyboard navigation.</li>
        <li>Review following the WCAG-EM 1.0 methodology.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    {/* 7 — Compatibility */}
    <section id="compatibility">
      <h2>7. Compatibility with browsers and assistive technologies</h2>
      <p>
        The site is designed to work with recent versions of the most widely used browsers
        (Chrome, Firefox, Safari and Edge) and with screen readers such as NVDA and VoiceOver.
        It is fully operable with the keyboard.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* 8 — Contact and feedback */}
    <section id="contact">
      <h2>8. Contact and feedback</h2>
      <p>
        Have you found an accessibility barrier or do you need content in an alternative format?
        Get in touch and we will help you:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Email:
          <a href="mailto:hola@caletasuites.com" aria-label="Send an email to hola@caletasuites.com">
            hola@caletasuites.com
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          Phone:
          <a href="tel:+34648789062" aria-label="Call +34 648 789 062">
            +34 648 789 062
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>We aim to respond within a maximum of 5 working days.</p>
    </section>

    {/* 9 — Complaints procedure */}
    <section id="complaints">
      <h2>9. Complaints procedure</h2>
      <p>
        If you are not satisfied after our response, you can file a complaint under Spanish Royal
        Decree 1112/2018 and Directive (EU) 2019/882 (the European Accessibility Act, applicable
        from 2025) with the competent body for digital accessibility.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* 10 — Metadata */}
    <section id="metadata">
      <h2>10. About this statement</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Statement date: {fechaLegible}.</li>
        <li>Standard applied: WCAG 2.2 level AA (fully conformant); colour contrast at level AAA.</li>
        <li>Responsible: Caleta Suites Tenerife.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
